---
title: Creamy Roasted Butternut Squash Curry with Chicken Breast with Tenderstem, Basmati Rice and Cashews
description: This Creamy Roasted Butternut Squash Curry is bursting full of flavours and makes a delicious dinner option from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!

Recipe Update: Due to quality issues with green beans, you'll instead receive Tenderstem® broccoli. As such, the recipe photos are slightly different to what your dish will look like. Don't worry, we've updated the instructions so it'll still be just as delicious!
